
# 1) Stop-sign arming uses the CURRENT SEGMENT MODE (route_modes[step]) instead of FSM state,
#    so it works even when you're in ROUTE dispatch or transitioning.
# 2) Stop-sign depth gate: NaN depth DOES NOT auto-reject (only rejects if finite and too far).
# 3) Adds STOP sign debug window drawing (box + distance text).
# 4) Traffic-light debounce is frozen while waiting (prevents flicker release).
#
# Keys:
#   Q / ESC : quit
#   T       : toggle RGB/BGR for camera frames
#   R       : re-prompt pickup/dropoff and re-plan
#   S       : emergency stop (goes IDLE)

